                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Two easy to get tradeable items are the Hammer of Wind and that fire wand off the pig herder in Tactics which both have Speed of Solsek on them which is 15% spell haste to detrimental spells which includes charm. I used the Tactics wand for a long time and it's an excellent tool for charm soloing. I'm not sure what they sell for server to server, but I know that I saw the Hammer of Wind selling for 15k on Seventh a few months ago which is relatively inexpensive I'd think for someone that can charm solo in PoP.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />When I was young I used to pray to God that He would give me a new bicycle. I soon found out that God didn't work that way, so I stole a bike and asked Him to forgive me.
